    <item>
      <title>乌克兰陆军参谋长准备好接受可能的法国军事训练员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/ukraine-army-chief-ready-for-possible-french-military-trainers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总司令亚历山大·西尔斯基表示，乌克兰正在为法国军事教官可能的首次访问做准备，政府要求北约盟国帮助训练基辅军队以对抗俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/ukraine-army-chief-ready-for-possible-french-military-trainers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 16:25:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗接近炸弹级的铀库存在选举前增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/iran-s-near-bomb-grade-uranium-stock-grows-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗增加了近乎炸弹级的铀库存，在德黑兰准备下个月举行总统选举之际，此举可能会加剧整个中东地区的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/iran-s-near-bomb-grade-uranium-stock-grows-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:47:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于担心遭到破坏，波兰将限制俄罗斯外交官的活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/poland-to-curb-russian-diplomat-movements-due-to-sabotage-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对涉嫌破坏活动的担忧日益加剧，波兰决定限制居住在其领土上的俄罗斯外交官的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/poland-to-curb-russian-diplomat-movements-due-to-sabotage-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家对匈牙利否决乌克兰武器援助感到愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/eu-nations-fume-over-hungary-s-vetoes-of-ukraine-weapons-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于乌克兰军队正在努力抵御俄罗斯的攻击，匈牙利拒绝向乌克兰提供超过 65 亿欧元（71 亿美元）的急需军事援助，这让欧盟成员国越来越恼火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/eu-nations-fume-over-hungary-s-vetoes-of-ukraine-weapons-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及士兵在拉法边境与以色列军队的冲突中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名埃及士兵在拉法边境口岸与以色列军队的冲突中丧生，这可能导致两国之间的紧张局势严重升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦将重振中国“一带一路”项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/pakistan-to-revive-china-belt-and-road-initiative-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦新政府希望为中国“一带一路”倡议下的项目注入新的动力，以提振该国陷入困境的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/pakistan-to-revive-china-belt-and-road-initiative-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:28:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界上任职时间最长的央行行长将在罗马尼亚获得新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚央行行长穆古尔·伊萨雷斯库 (Mugur Isarescu) 是全球任职时间最长的央行行长，他将获得新一届五年任期，议会希望在 6 月底前就延长任期进行表决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基访问期间西班牙承诺提供10亿欧元军事援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/zelenskiy-to-sign-security-deal-with-spain-during-madrid-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基与西班牙签署了一项安全协议，其中涉及今年 10 亿欧元（11 亿美元）的军事物资，以援助基辅的战争努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/zelenskiy-to-sign-security-deal-with-spain-during-madrid-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:03:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙和朔尔茨计划联手加强欧洲防空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/macron-scholz-plan-european-air-defense-push-during-state-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国计划于本周公布加强欧洲防空合作的计划，以应对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰后要求欧洲人致力于自身安全的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/macron-scholz-plan-european-air-defense-push-during-state-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 08:49:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁不受欢迎的领导人创下新低：支持率仅为 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/peru-s-unpopular-leader-hits-new-low-a-5-approval-rating</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁的迪娜·博卢阿特 (Dina Boluarte) 的支持率跌至新低，只有 5% 的人表示在国家政治动荡中支持总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/peru-s-unpopular-leader-hits-new-low-a-5-approval-rating</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
